item.title: CVE-2021-21532|2024-09-16T17:28:09.912Z -- dell -- wyse%20proprietary%20os%20%28thinos%29
item.description: Dell Wyse ThinOS 8.6 MR9 contains remediation for an improper management server validation vulnerability that could be potentially exploited to redirect a client to an attacker-controlled management server, thus allowing the attacker to change the device configuration or certificate file.
